<p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 30px 20px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 609.292px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.25714em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">为营造良好的校园氛围，创建干净整洁的校园环境，进一步</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">改善</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">经济管理学院公共卫生</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">环境</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">。经济管理学院第29期入党积极分子和第30期入党积极分子于2023年12月9日共同开展了学院仓库清扫活动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.25714em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705117073995047304.jpg" title="1705117073995047304.jpg" alt="143642883507b523eee4c62fd5926d0d.jpg" width="884" height="431" style="width: 884px; height: 431px;"/></span></p></section></section></section></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.1142px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">活动开始前，学工办主任郭伟老师对本次活动进行了安排部署,强调了清扫活动的注意事项和打扫要求。入党积极分子们纷纷表示一定会认真打扫学院仓库，这体现了新时代大学生不怕脏、不怕苦、不怕累的精神风貌。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.1142px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.1142px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">分工明确后，入党积极分子们齐心协力地把仓库堆积物品搬至仓库门口，仔细地把仓库物品分类并摆放整齐，用他们的实际行动体现了他们认真负责，甘于奉献的精神态度。</span></span></p>